name: Ineda Systems
overview:
Ineda Systems (pronounced “E-ne-da”) is a startup company that was created by industry veterans from US and India with an ultimate goal of becoming a leader in developing low power SOC’s for the use in both consumer and enterprise applications. The advisory and management team has world-class experience of working in both blue chip companies as well as fast paced technology start-ups. Ineda’s expertise is in the area of low-power SOC/IP development, architecture, and software that is necessary to design silicon & systems that would be of use in future applications.

Our products will address the wearable platforms from a ground-up manner including vertical engineering of the wearable device: silicon, system, software, application ecosystem. In addition, we will enable the ecosystem with API’s and the application development framework. In combination with our leading edge technology, Ineda silicon will be the first in the world with power usage in the envelope required by wearable devices.
